'''East Ryloth Street''' was located within the city of [[Xakrea]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Darkknell/Legends|Darkknell]]. The roadway was at least five kilometers long and was where [[Arky's Emporium of Forgotten Treasures]] was situated.

Considered part of a seedy neighborhood, properties on that street were held with lower regard compared to those on its counterpart, [[West Ryloth Street]].

